			<h4> Our moods dictate how we interpret our experiences.</h4>
			<h5> The Mood-O-Meter app makes it easy for you to record exactly how you feel and what actions contributed to your state-of-mind from your morning routine to your daily workload to your wild nights out. By recording your mood on a regular basis you give yourself the opportunity to improve your quality of life in a free and easy way.  </h5>
