				<h2 class="textTitle">  How this works: </h2>
			</div>
				<br>
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<p> 1. Fill out a short checklist to identify daily activities and their correlation to your daily mood. </p>
				<br>
				<p> 2. On a scale of 1-10 rate your degree of happines for the day. Make sure to consider your whole day and not just a fleeting emotion, this will help to increase the accuracy of your the correlations we draw between your activities and your mood.</p>
				<br>
				<p> 3. Write a short entry that personalizes your current mood. When you check out your responses over the course of a few weeks this information will allow you to more accurately reflect on how and why you feel the way you do. </p>
